main event: Three round bluish-orange objects were observed for 8 minutes in Fall City, Texas.
interesting points: The objects were seen at army strength and moved out of sight in a straight line at high speed., The sighting event was captured using ground-radar and air-intercept radar., The length of observation was precisely noted to be 8 minutes., The report was part of Project Blue Book, indicating official interest in UFO phenomena., The conclusion stated that the objects were probably aircraft.
